ServiceNow

ServiceNow API for accessing the Service-now platform.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install
	
To install this module in a windows O.S. we have tested dmake module:
	
	perl Makefile.PL
	dmake
	dmake test
	dmake install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc ServiceNow

